  "general_provisions": "This bill creates a grant program to provide internet connectivity on school buses in rural school districts.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>creates a grant program for rural school districts to install and operate internet connectivity systems on school buses;<hr><ltbullet>establishes priority criteria for awarding grants;<hr><ltbullet>allows districts to combine grant money with district funds;<hr><ltbullet>requires grant recipients to commit to long-term operation of internet connectivity systems; and<hr><ltbullet>requires the State Board of Education to make rules for grant administration.",
